snippet.textDisplay: At first I was angry that they want me to pay more for Sword and Shield, but then I realized I would much rather pay $30 for these passes and start receiving the content in June instead of waiting the whole year and paying $60 for the exact same content like I was expecting to. Plus, you don't even the passes to trade and transfer the old Pokemon that are in them, so if that's all you were looking for, you'll only have to pay for Pokemon HOME (unless you get everything from trading, of course).
